stringToLowerCase**src/Haskell/Basic.hs:.stringified_code:
stringToLowerCase
  = map toLower
  where
      toLower c
        | 'A' <= c && c <= 'Z' = toEnum (fromEnum c + 32)
        | otherwise = c

stringToUpperCase**src/Haskell/Basic.hs:.stringified_code:
stringToUpperCase
  = map toUpper
  where
      toUpper c
        | 'a' <= c && c <= 'z' = toEnum (fromEnum c - 32)
        | otherwise = c
